      <div class="interact"><div class="interact-emoji">😂</div><div><div style="display:flex;align-items:center"><h3>Emoji Reacts</h3><span class="rate">30%</span></div><p>Taps a random emoji reaction on stories: laughing, love, fire, surprised, crying, or clapping.</p></div></div>
